# [span_106](start_span)TLP / power-profiles-daemon: energy-saving profile[span_106](end_span)
exec --no-startup-id powerprofilesctl set power-saver 2>/dev/null \
     [span_107](start_span)|| tlp bat 2>/dev/null || true[span_107](end_span)

# [span_108](start_span)NVIDIA: сбросить контроль вентилятора на автоматический[span_108](end_span)
[span_109](start_span)exec --no-startup-id nvidia-settings -a "[gpu:0]/GPUFanControlState=0" 2>/dev/null || true[span_109](end_span)

# [span_110](start_span)── Idle & Lock ──────────────────────────────────────────────[span_110](end_span)
exec --no-startup-id swayidle -w \
    timeout 300  'swaylock -f -c 000000 --font monospace' \
    timeout 600  'swaymsg "output * dpms off"' \
    resume       'swaymsg "output * dpms on"' \
    [span_111](start_span)before-sleep 'swaylock -f -c 000000 --font monospace'[span_111](end_span)

